title: 이달의소녀탐구 #275 (LOONA TV #275)
summary:
0:01 -- Yves PD!
0:13 -- Yves takes audience to Go Won’s prep room and shows her dress. She also has
her own transition.
0:26 -- Go Won: “I’m 170cm right now~” (with heels).
Yves: ”Chuu, stand next to her!”, Chuu: “No~!!” (our short but cute queen)
0:33 -- Go Won repeatedly says that she is nervous.
0:42 -- “Chuu PD!” “Chuu PD!” (Yves mentions that Chuu should’ve said Yves PD!)
0:55 -- Yves (looking at Go Won dancing): She is bouncing like Kong kong! Kong Won!”
